Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.14,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,"EPISODE 3: REUNI"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:21.98,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,MIYAKOJIMA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.77,0:00:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyakojima menguasai pertandingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyakojima memang hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Miyakojima Narika dari kelas B.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia terkenal di sekolah ini,\Nmeski tak seterkenal Konohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang kau lihat,\Ndia hebat dalam olahraga,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sekaligus siswi tomboi\Npaling cantik di akademi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren apanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ada satu hal yang sangat mencolok.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejujurnya, dia agak sulit didekati.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada banyak rumor tentangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang bilang keluarganya itu yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi teringat ucapan Tuan Kagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menyelidiki keluargamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.06,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Putri Keluarga Miyakojima\Njuga bersekolah di Akademi Kiou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau tak punya\Ndendam pribadi dengan keluarganya,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi cari aman saja, jauhi dia\Nkecuali benar-benar mendesak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki! Aku rindu padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Narika...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuceritakan sedikit\Ntentang masa laluku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu sekali,\NKeluarga Miyakojima yang merawatku.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rich Girl Caretaker:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:03:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I'm Secretly the Caregiver of the\NMost Popular Girl in This Rich Kid School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedua orang tuaku parah, tapi mereka rukun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, pernah sekali\Nmereka membahas soal perceraian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat aku berumur sepuluh tahun,\Nibuku membawaku pergi dari rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lalu kami tinggal di rumah mendiang nenekku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu adalah rumah Keluarga Miyakojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka benar-benar tak tahu malu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap mereka tak membawa\Npengaruh buruk bagi Nona Narika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku baru tahu hal ini belakangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi nenekku sudah putus hubungan\Ndengan Keluarga Miyakojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, ibuku memaksa untuk kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak laki-laki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Tomonari Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tinggal di sini sejak kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benci orang lemah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah dengar soal dirimu\Ndari para pelayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dan ibumu cuma parasit yang tak berguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku akan memberimu pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini, kau yang mengurusku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adalah putri tunggal\NKeluarga Miyakojima, Narika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak hari itu, aku hampir selalu\Nberada di sisinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki! Ada serangga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya. Biar kusingkirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki! Ayah memarahiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya, pasti rasanya kesal sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki, kau lebih kuat dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak menangis saat lihat serangga,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tak gentar sedikit pun\Nsaat dimarahi orang dewasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, begitulah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebagai penerus Keluarga Miyakojima,\Naku ingin jadi lebih kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku penakut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Umurku sepuluh tahun, tapi keluar rumah\Nsendirian saja aku tak berani.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kecil Narika dijejali doktrin\Nbahwa dunia luar itu berbahaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sehingga dia takut pergi keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku melihatnya beberapa hari yang lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada seorang gadis berjalan sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seandainya saja\Naku punya keberanian seperti dia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, mau coba\Npergi keluar bersamaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat! Hebat! Hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bebas seperti burung!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Toko jajanan. Boleh kita ke sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.44,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki, apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu stik Yumbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itulah, namanya Yumbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak saat itu,\Nkami sering menyelinap keluar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghabiskan waktu sejenak di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, waktu bermain kami akhirnya ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya kau menyeret putriku keluar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena dianggap membahayakan Narika,\Naku dan ibuku diusir dari rumah Miyakojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berjanji akan jadi lebih kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.02,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki, Itsuki, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakiku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saking senangnya, kakiku sampai lemas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kau akan baikan\Nsetelah istirahat sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi dulu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tinggalkan aku di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf dulu aku ceroboh\Nmenyeretmu keluar saat kita masih kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa harus minta maaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru aku berterima kasih padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu itu, seandainya aku\Ntidak keluar bersamamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku takkan pernah bisa\Nmengalahkan rasa takutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, sekarang kau tak penakut lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.41,0:07:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku masih dalam tahap latihan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku payah dalam hal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku payah mencari teman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya banyak orang yang salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar! Semuanya salah sangka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kok bisa begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluarga Miyakojima\Nsangat menjunjung tinggi ilmu bela diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kecil, aku sudah digembleng\Nberbagai macam bela diri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, tradisi itu malah membuat orang\Nmenganggap keluarga kami militan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Militan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}S-Selain itu, karena ini kau\Nmakanya aku berani bilang,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau sedang gugup, wajahku jadi tegang,\Ndan itu membuat orang ketakutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tahu-tahu, mereka menjulukiku macam-macam,\Nmulai dari preman sampai yakuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong, Itsuki! Bantu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku sih ingin membantu, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku harus angkat telepon dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Itsuki, Anda di mana sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada murid pingsan,\Njadi aku membawanya ke UKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya khawatir terjadi sesuatu\Nkarena lokasi Anda
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berbeda dengan lokasi Nona.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong segera kembali ke kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Membantu orang lain itu bagus,\Ntapi jangan lupakan tugas Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang apa kau di akademi ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu, ceritanya panjang...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Narika, aku harus pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.70,0:08:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau takkan menghilang lagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan khawatir. Kita akan bertemu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.17,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tepuk kepalaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu kau sering melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini memang bikin aku tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf ya, waktu itu aku tiba-tiba menghilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang penting kita sudah bertemu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang kalian lakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.07,0:09:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Konohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa agak tidak enak badan,\Njadi aku izin ke UKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi pada kalian berdua,\NTomonari, Miyakojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku melihatnya pingsan di lorong,\Njadi kubawa ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:10:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kepalamu terbentur, Miyakojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi kulihat dia menepuk kepalamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, dia melihatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Konohana, dengarkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dan Itsuki sudah saling kenal sejak lama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak lama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu umur kami sepuluh tahun,\NItsuki tinggal di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal di sana?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.29,0:10:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu Itsuki yang mengurusku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengurus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain, aku berutang budi padanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.36,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makanya aku senang bisa bertemu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau datang ke rumahku lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa main ke sana,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}a-atau kalau mau,\Nkita bisa kembali seperti dulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Narika, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tidak mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, Tomonari bekerja di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hina... Konohana, kau tak boleh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang itu kenyataannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sudah sepakat\Nmerahasiakannya, lalu kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-A-Apa maksudnya ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, maksudnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, pekerjaan utamaku\Nadalah menjadi pengurus pribadinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.06,0:11:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Curang...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau curang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak akan kalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki itu awalnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.92,0:11:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak tahu masa lalu kalian,\Ntapi Tomonari kini bekerja di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tomonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyakojima sepertinya sudah baikan,\Nmungkin sebaiknya kau kembali ke kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Y-Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga sudah pulih, jadi aku pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, Narika. Saat ini, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pura-pura sakit\Nhanya untuk mencariku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pasti tersesat kalau sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku pura-pura sakit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan minta diantar seseorang\Nsampai separuh jalan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah membuatmu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa kau beri tahu dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya hubungan kita harus dirahasiakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma berpikir...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebaiknya kuperingatkan dia dari awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah dia cemburu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ini pengurus siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini, aku pengurusmu, Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizune bisa marah pada kita berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau aku dipecat gara-gara ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak akan memecatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari ceritamu, Nona juga bersalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah tahu kalau Anda\Ndan Nona Miyakojima pernah kenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi hasil selidik kami tidak mengungkap
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bahwa kalian sedekat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.29,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita harus cari cara untuk menjelaskan ini\Nkepada Nona Miyakojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Itsuki, tolong bicaralah dengannya\Ndan minta dia merahasiakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, Nona...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda menempel terus padanya seperti koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa gerangan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}E-Entah apa yang merasukinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepuk aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.87,0:13:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepuk kepalaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.44,0:13:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat atas kepindahanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga harimu\Nmenyenangkan ke depannya, Tomonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru pertama kali aku ikut pesta teh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa sangka aku bakal semeja dengan mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua ini bermula tadi pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau pesta penyambutanmu\Ndiadakan pulang sekolah ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, ya. Hari ini aku bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, kau bebas ajak\Nsiapa saja yang kau mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Acaranya di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kupikirkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang ingin kuundang?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya pesta teh,\Ntapi lokasinya di kafe sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, meski sudah dapat izin\Ndari Shizune, kau itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan tanya sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona, ada yang bisa kubantu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin ikut pesta teh bersama Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya tak masalah\Nselama Tuan Itsuki mendampingi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Anda tidak masalah dengan itu, Nona?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya ini hampir...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, ini demi bersosialisasi,\Njadi jangan terlalu dipaksakan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau ikut, aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.55,0:14:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya dia ingin cari teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Kau mau apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan aku sedang senggang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bersedia membicarakan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal apa yang terjadi\Ndengan Konohana kemarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga! Aku belum memaafkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar pengkhianat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku ingin tinggal bersamamu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.28,0:15:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku tidak bilang apa-apa barusan!\NLupakan saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, tenang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkatnya, aku diadopsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diadopsi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah baruku adalah direktur\Nanak perusahaan Grup Konohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat koneksi itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku magang di Keluarga Konohana\Nuntuk belajar tata krama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Magang?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu, kau tinggal dengan mereka\Nsebagai sarana pembelajaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuharap kau bisa merahasiakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjadi anak angkat\Npastilah posisi yang sulit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, apa kau ada\Nwaktu luang sepulang sekolah hari ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.48,0:15:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pulang sekolah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau ikut datang ke pesta teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}P-Pesta teh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mau ikut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia menangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu ingin ikut pesta teh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak pernah ada yang mengajakku\Nke acara semacam itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi apa kau yakin tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kehadiranku takkan membuat\Nsuasananya jadi canggung?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, pasti tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus bergegas kembali ke kelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, murid pindahan tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah dengar semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kenal dengan Konohana Hinako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau itu anggota Faksi Konohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Faksi Konohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.27,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semacam klub penggemar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eum, Tennoji, apa jangan-jangan\Nkau membenci Konohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku takkan bilang aku membencinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengakui penuh\Nkemampuan Konohana Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilan dan kemampuan akademisnya\Nsetara denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cara menghibur diri yang cukup unik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, kenapa semua orang\Nharus begitu memujanya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.56,0:17:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa karena dia terlihat lebih ramah dariku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia selalu tebar senyum sana-sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gadis ini rupanya cuma memikirkan Hinako...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eum, ada rencana pesta teh\Npulang sekolah nanti...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tomonari, bagaimana kau\Nbisa mengenal mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kau bisa akrab\Ndengan para superstar ini
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}padahal baru hari ketiga pindah ke sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eum, kebetulan saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Izinkan aku\Nmemperkenalkan diri dengan sopan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Tennoji Mirei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku putri dari Grup Tennoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Taisho Katsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargaku berbisnis di industri pelayaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Asahi Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargaku berbisnis retail,\Nkhususnya toko elektronik.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Konohana Hinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku Miyakojima Narika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}S-Senang...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia jadi kacau...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Tomonari Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keluargaku berkecimpung di bisnis IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kujelaskan dari awal bahwa\Nlatar belakang keluargaku itu tidak penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sungkan\Nuntuk mengobrol santai denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, akan kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga jangan terlalu gugup, Narika.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tentu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau baru saja memanggilnya Narika?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, eum, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.01,0:18:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}D-Dulu saat umurku sepuluh tahun,\Naku bertemu Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itulah alasannya dia mengundangku\Nke pesta teh ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kalian salah paham,\Ntapi Narika bukan orang yang menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu kecil, dia menghabiskan\Nsebagian besar waktunya di rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makanya dia kurang luwes bergaul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua rumor tentangnya itu bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa benar begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:19:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar keluargamu itu produsen\Nalat olahraga ya, Miyakojima?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tak kusangka kau tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlalu merendah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak ada seorang pun di sini
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang belum pernah mendengar\Nnama Keluarga Miyakojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, setelah sedikit riset,\Njelas saja rumor itu cuma omong kosong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Miyakojima, apa yang biasanya\Nkau lakukan di waktu luang?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}B-Biasanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.86,0:19:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berlatih di rumah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berlatih?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada dojo di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rutinitasku sehari-hari\Nadalah latihan di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedengarannya sangat menyehatkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Konohana, apa kau menghabiskan\Nseluruh waktumu untuk belajar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, belajar itu memang penting,\Ntapi aku juga butuh istirahat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya bersantai sambil makan camilan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.98,0:19:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kau suka ngemil, Konohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Camilan seperti apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Scone, kurasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya keripik kentang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tomonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat minum teh, akan terlihat lebih anggun\Njika kau mendekatkan cangkir ke bibirmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu. Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tomonari, sebelum ini, apa kau\Nbersekolah di SMA biasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu sebabnya\Ntata krama bukanlah keahlianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi SMA biasa punya\Ntradisi yang unik, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, numpang makan, patungan,\Ndan jam makan siang lebih awal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak bisa disebut tradisi, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tahu kebiasaan unik\Nsemacam itu lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba kupikirkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, aturan belum tiga detik?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aturan belum tiga menit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kutunjukkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu adalah aturan yang bilang kalau makanan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih aman dimakan\Njika jatuhnya belum tiga detik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata rakyat biasa sekreatif itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka malah terkesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.37,0:20:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, sebaiknya jangan ditiru...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:21:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.64,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menarik sih,\Ntapi menurutku itu agak tidak higienis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Itu benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.21,0:21:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awalnya aku khawatir, tapi syukurlah\Nmereka semua bisa menikmatinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.75,0:21:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita adakan pesta teh bersama lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konohana Hinako!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.19,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}I-Ini pertama kalinya aku ikut\Npesta teh eksklusif bersamamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi ternyata acaranya tak seburuk dugaanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kita harus kumpul-kumpul lagi\Nkapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}L-Lalu, Tomonari.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kulihat kau mulai menjaga\Npostur tubuhmu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jadi kelihatan lebih menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pergi dulu ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Kau tidak dijemput, Narika?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mobilku terjebak macet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya sudah dekat,\Njadi aku akan jalan ke sana sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku bisa mengantarmu ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}T-Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizune, bolehkah\Naku mengantar Narika ke mobilnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah Anda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda tak keberatan, Nona?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.50,0:22:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya aku bisa bernapas lega!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa mengobrol\Ndengan semua orang dengan luwes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku takkan bisa melakukannya\Ntanpa bantuan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tidak ada kau, aku akan\Njadi penyendiri sampai lulus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.25,0:22:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tidak begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma memberimu dorongan kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku mengenal diriku sendiri\Nlebih baik dari siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:22:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini adalah hari yang mengubah hidupku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.86,0:23:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau akan selalu jadi pahlawanku, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Narika...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya ini curang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.26,0:23:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Curang, curang!\NKonohana curang!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih bahas soal itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.46,0:23:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita 'kan akhirnya bisa bertemu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.36,0:23:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus, kenapa kau tinggal di rumah Konohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Duh, aku harus bilang apa, ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan masa magangmu selesai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, saat ini sih,\Nbelum ada tanda-tanda selesai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.66,0:23:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}K-Kalau masa magangmu sudah selesai,\Nmaukah kau kerja di tempatku?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, nanti kupikirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu namanya janji palsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itsuki!
